query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(t1 tq1 s) */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('avfoundation',
'jboss7.x',
'knockout.js',
'refactoring',
'sql-server-2008',
'transactions')
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow',
'superuser')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id
inner join question AS q1
on a1.question_id = q1.id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 100 AND q1.view_count <= 100000
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 0 AND u1.upvotes <= 1 group by t1.name;
